{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-281-pizza-toppings","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 281: Sastojci za picu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Daje vam se pizza (savršen krug) koja je isečena na jednake komade $m \\cdot n$ i želite da na svakom komadu imate samo jednu komponentu.</p>\n<p>Neka je $f(m,n)$ broj načina na koje možete rasporediti dodatke na picu ako imate $m$ različitih dodataka ($m \\ge 2$), koristeći svaki dodatak na $n$ kriški tačno ($n \\ge 1$). Odbijanje (refleksije) se smatra različitim, rotacije ne.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $f(2,1) = 1$, $f(2,2) = f(3,1) = 2$ i $f(3,2) = 16$. $f(3,2)$ je prikazano ispod:</p>\n<img alt=\"animation with 16 ways to have 3 different toppings on 2 slices each\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/pizza-toppings.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Pronađite skup svih $f(m,n)$ za koje je $f(m,n) ≤ {10}^{15}$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4861000cf542c50ff98","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301932,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-281-pizza-toppings"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function pizzaToppings() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npizzaToppings();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>pizzaToppings()</code> treba da vrati <code>1485776387445623</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(p